    <note>Shang(1) Qi [17640] This Shang(1) family seems to be a gentry lineage of Yiwu that has no recorded Song jinshi. They may be related to the Linhai Shang(1). In order to establish the intermarriage links, I am assuming that Yu(9) Shi's [17639] son-in-law, Shang(1) Kezhong [17641] and Qi were cousins. Qi's son-in-law, Yu(9) Xian [17647], was Yu(9) Shi's grandson. Chen Liang, WJ, 29.1b-2a (wife, born Chen, who married him at age 17 and died in 1173 at age 48).</note>
